<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Name your list - publishthis.email</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/view.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Martel:300,400|Open+Sans:300,400,600|Roboto+Slab:300,400" rel="stylesheet">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-margin page">
    <h1>Give your list a name!</h1>
    <div class="name-form form">
      <input id="name" class="input-border" placeholder="List name"/>
      <div class="form-button" onclick="save()">Save</div>
    </div>
    <p>Give your list a name to help your subscribers understand more about your list.</p>
    <p>Your list name will appear in the subscription box for new subscribers and as the "from" name when you send a new post to your subscribers.</p>
  </div>
  [[= partial('partials/analytics.dot') ]]
</body>
</html>
